If I where 25 I would be married and I got up on Wendnesday morning at half past five ready to go to work I started out once more to the steal works where. I had worked for five years I went down the same old Streets until I came to the works I had to work from half past six in the morning till 3 o, clock in the afternoon after a weeks work all the men would go to the big room at the back of the works to get our pay we got xxxx22 pound a week I would have a good life with 2 children even a that age I Would Still be interested in cricket, Football, and swimming any time I had a day of I would let my wife go out and I would stay and look after the children.  Words: 146
